---

<section style="
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--strata-blue) 0%, var(--strata-dark) 100%);
  color: white;
  padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
">
  <div style="max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
    ">
      The Modern <span style="color: #b3d9ff;">Type-Safe</span> Language
    </h1>
    
    <p style="
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      opacity: 0.95;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    ">
      Strata brings together the power of compiled languages with the simplicity of modern scripting.
    </p>

    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
      <a href="https://docs.strata-lang.dev/getting-started/quick-start" style="
        background: white;
        color: var(--strata-blue);
        padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        transition: all 0.2s;
      " onmouseenter="this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2)'" onmouseleave="this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.boxShadow='none'">
        Get Started
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/VSS-CO/Strata" style="
        background: transparent;
        color: white;
        padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
        border: 2px solid white;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        transition: all 0.2s;
      " onmouseenter="this.style.background='white'; this.style.color='var(--strata-blue)'" onmouseleave="this.style.background='transparent'; this.style.color='white'">
        View on GitHub
      </a>
    </div>

    <div style="
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    ">
      <div>
        <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">50+</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.875rem; opacity: 0.9;">Language Features</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">100%</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.875rem; opacity: 0.9;">Type Safe</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Zero</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.875rem; opacity: 0.9;">Overhead</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
